esian coordinates</h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-edit=
section-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?ti=
tle=3DCylindrical_coordinate_system&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D5" titl=
e=3D"Edit section: Cartesian coordinates"><span>edit</span></a><span class=
